## Apple Pie
This app show cases the skills that I have learned thoughout the App Development with Swift course and how I am able
to apply the design principles ton create a visually appealing exerience.
The app can be downloaded here: [link](https://github.com/jacksdre/portfolio/blob/master/Apple%20Pie.xcodeproj.zip)

Use of multiple views, layering button grids and image views, while constraining them to fit and size ipad.

updating UI as player makes moves,every button pressed is disabled and, each wrong answer drops a an apple and each correct
answer reveals a letter of the word to be guessed.
